>>36ecb380-3d45-42c1-8026-efdaa77244cc
https://www.strongfirst.com/blog/
https://www.strongfirst.com/product-category/books/
Try bodyweight and kettlebells if you can. StrongFirst is a good start, Pavel creates minimalist and effective programs. Avoid CrossFit, it's full of shit, and follow a program with a great discipline (you'll probably lost your time if you tweak it without a good understanding of what you're doing). Consistency and simplicity are the keys to progress.

They don't care if that's not against the ToS. They do whatever they want to do, you're powerless against them unless you're very popular. They locked me for "hate speech" even though it wasn't (I said that the idea of transsexuality implies the existence of at least two sexes). I appealed the lock and they told me, 2 months later, that yes, this is "hate speech" according to their ToS (which is untrue).
